headline: Walgreens Boots Alliance Adjusts Fiscal 2025 First Quarter Earnings Announcement to be Held on January 10
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., January 02, 2025--Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc. (Nasdaq: WBA) will release its fiscal year 2025 first quarter results at 7 a.m. ET on Friday, January 10, followed by a one-hour conference call with WBA management beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET.
